    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《喵语咖啡》邀请你走进一家温馨可爱的猫咖世界。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将会化身店主Lucy，一边经营管理猫咪咖啡馆，为客人端上有猫咖特色的咖啡与甜点，解锁食物、家具和猫窝，一边走上纽约的大街小巷拯救流浪猫，为它们提供庇护所，并为它们牵线找到幸福的新家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159560/extras/a92667da57480a9be1d60d4ee6ed4db5.poster.avif?t=1759765410\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159560/extras/a92667da57480a9be1d60d4ee6ed4db5.webm?t=1759765410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159560/extras/a92667da57480a9be1d60d4ee6ed4db5.mp4?t=1759765410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身纽约猫奴Lucy，开启你的猫咖冒险之旅吧！🐾</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这座城市里，你将寻找并拯救各种各样的萌萌的小猫咪，每只都有自己独特的性格和故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159560/extras/df0830b1f225efe2a3cc22d4b03badeb.poster.avif?t=1759765410\" width=538 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159560/extras/df0830b1f225efe2a3cc22d4b03badeb.webm?t=1759765410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159560/extras/df0830b1f225efe2a3cc22d4b03badeb.mp4?t=1759765410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将把它们安置在你的猫咖啡馆里，精心照顾，再为它们牵线完美的铲屎官，帮它们找到真正的“永远的家”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159560/extras/e26a0e5c3a7dc8f3488d509f65368803.poster.avif?t=1759765410\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159560/extras/e26a0e5c3a7dc8f3488d509f65368803.webm?t=1759765410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159560/extras/e26a0e5c3a7dc8f3488d509f65368803.mp4?t=1759765410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邂逅形形色色的客人，与他们展开走心对话，倾听属于他们的故事，一起编织属于大家的猫咖成长旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159560/extras/4213613e9d1365209bfc9c4500cd4069.poster.avif?t=1759765410\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159560/extras/4213613e9d1365209bfc9c4500cd4069.webm?t=1759765410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159560/extras/4213613e9d1365209bfc9c4500cd4069.mp4?t=1759765410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断升级菜单，解锁更多美味餐点、室内装扮和猫咪专属好物，为你的猫咖添一份温暖与惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一场充满爱与欢笑的治愈冒险，每一次相遇都可能改变一只猫的命运。 作为猫咖老板的你，准备好了吗？从一只只小猫开始，去温暖整个世界吧！🐾</p>",
